data.title: Cosworth Story
data.meta_description: Cosworth Story - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document summarizes the unique success of the Cosworth DFV Grand Prix engine over 16 years from 1967-1983. It provided the basis for 9 driver championships and 5 constructor championships, winning 154 races. The DFV was normally aspirated but was eventually displaced by 1.5L turbocharged engines requiring 5 years of development. The document also provides background on Cosworth Engineering and the technical advances of the predecessor Cosworth FVA engine which informed the design of the landmark DFV engine.
